<p class="govuk-body-l">Trade remedies, also known as trade defence measures, are trade policy tools which allow the UK to protect domestic industries from unfair competition from products imported from other countries.</p>

<h2 class="gem-c-contents-list__title">Contents</h2>
<ol class="gem-c-contents-list__list govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">

